What is the setup? The instance is configured behind a private network using Gitlab Omnibus configuration, and the sub-domain is provisioned by an Apache configuration on another server. So the SSL certificates are tied to the Apache server&rsquo;s IP address. The certificates are provided by letsencrypt.
